data.description: WELCOME HOME - Time to own a piece of coutry paradise!! This amazing home is only 5 years old and consists of 3 bdrms and 2.5 baths.  You will find in this beautiful home LVP flooring, a rock fireplace with gas logs, granite counter tops, 9ft ceilings, oversized garage, a split bedroom floorplan with a large open concept  LR/DR/Kitchen for family and/or entertaining. It boasts over 29 acres of beautiful mature trees, trails, abundant wildlife, a creek and a 40x25 barn with power.   In the Kitchen you will find a large pantry and beautiful oversized island with lots of natural light. The spacious Master Bedroom has 2 WIC, soak your cares away in the garden tub and separate shower.
